Detailed Description

Subversion's working copy library.

Requires:

  • A working copy

Provides:

  • Ability to manipulate working copy's versioned data.
  • Ability to manipulate working copy's administrative files.

Used By:

  • Clients.

Definition in file svn_wc.h.
